item.title: Features
item.dc:creator: oye
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row css_animation="fadeIn"][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Unique WooCommerce Features

[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50" css=".vc_custom_1485783098332{margin-top: 0px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap="20" equal_height="yes"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783295957{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="347" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="WooCommerce One Page Shopping" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

WooCommerce One Page Shopping. Supercharge your store with this plugin. Use AngularJS to load WooCommerce template super fast so user do not wait to see your products and checkout quickly.

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Demo" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#222222" outline_custom_hover_background="#222222" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" align="center" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Foyetheme.nmediahosting.com%2Fone-page-woostore%2F|title:One%20Page%20Shopping||"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783301148{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="343" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="WooCommerce Product Designer" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

Product Designer is a simple and light weight plugin for heavy work. Admin can set templates like T-Shirt, Mugs. User design product from library images or text or even upload his own file. Save it and checkout.

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Demo" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#222222" outline_custom_hover_background="#222222" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" align="center" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Foyetheme.nmediahosting.com%2Fproduct%2Fcustom-shirt%2F|||"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783306735{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="356" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="Personalized Product Option" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

WooCommerce Personalized Product Option Plugin can add 14 types of input fields on product page. Client personalized these product like choose a color for T-Shirt, add text on Mug, upload design for Visiting Cards etc before checkout. The best part of this plugin is image/file upload control with cropping options.

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Demo" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#222222" outline_custom_hover_background="#222222" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" align="center" link="url:https%3A%2F%2Fnajeebmedia.com%2Fwordpress-plugin%2Fwoocommerce-personalized-product-option%2F||target:%20_blank|"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap="20" equal_height="yes"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783245788{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="360" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="WooCommerce Checkout Fields Editor" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

This plugin can control all field on checkout page. Even default billing and shipping fields can be edit, re-order or delete. More fields can also be added in three areas of checkout page like Billing, Shipping and after Order Notes. Also file/image can also be uploaded.

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Demo" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#222222" outline_custom_hover_background="#222222" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" align="center" link="url:https%3A%2F%2Fnajeebmedia.com%2Fwordpress-plugin%2Fwoocommerce-checkout-field-editor-plugin%2F||target:%20_blank|"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783253330{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="363" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="WP User Registration" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

WP User Registration Form render WordPress signup form based on fields selected by Admin. Input fields can be placed in registration form using nice drag and drop meta page. Four fields are set to default as per required by WP Core these are: User Name, Email First and Last name. Once user is registered emails sent with login detail.

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Demo" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#222222" outline_custom_hover_background="#222222" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" align="center" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Foyetheme.nmediahosting.com%2Fregistration%2F|||"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783260693{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="365" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="File Upload and Manager" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

File Upload and Downloadis simply the best WordPress Front End plugin allow users, clients or members to upload and manage files of any type like PDF, Images, Docs, Sheets, Videos etc.Admin can download, view all uploaded images uploaded users and more

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Demo" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#222222" outline_custom_hover_background="#222222" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" align="center" link="url:https%3A%2F%2Fnajeebmedia.com%2Fwordpress-plugin%2Fwp-front-end-file-upload-and-download-manager%2F||target:%20_blank|"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="fadeIn" css=".vc_custom_1485783516365{margin-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Unique Theme Features

[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50" css=".vc_custom_1485783098332{margin-top: 0px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap="20" equal_height="yes"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783245788{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="384" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="Header Design " font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]
    • Unlimited color variation
    • Background image
    • Google fonts
    • Background images and color
    • Sticky header

Control layout globally / single

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783253330{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="363" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="WooCommerce Store Customizer" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

WooCommerce Store Customizer plugin can change labels for different area in WooCommere, Add contents using Hooks. Product Tabs can also be added with this. And Enquiry Tab can also be added against all Products.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInDown" width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1485783260693{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_single_image image="365" img_size="full" alignment="center"][vc_custom_heading text="Redux Options Framework " font_container="tag:h2|font_size:25|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_separator color="custom" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#fb3d50"][vc_column_text]

Redux is built for WordPress. Why? Because we firmly believe that WordPress is the most solid platform currently available and want to help plugin and theme developers release better creations faster! Aren't familiar with WordPress yet? You're probably in the wrong place... but you might want to stop by the Codex.. it provides a wealth of knowledge to help you get on your feed!.
